{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_2000-06-09-1",
 "title": "A Helpful Racer at the Swoop Arena",
 "summary": "At the Reckless Abandon Swoop Arena on Corellia, the disguised agent Bazil McKenzie -- in his black-clad swooper guise of Mege Vauki, racing Grade One for team KIF -- grumbles with fellow racers while waiting for swoops to arrive. Leaving the staging area, he encounters a curious, lost newcomer, the tattooed Meditersarian Luther Syss, who asks directions to the spectator stands. Bazil obligingly escorts Luther through the concourse, pointing out the escalators to the viewing stands, and the two exchange names and friendly words. Luther wishes him luck in the upcoming Saturday race, and Bazil invites him to the post-race awards aboard the Rancor before the two part ways amid the arena crowds.",
